    {
      "bookmarkId": "24275985_36_4404-4432",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "4404-4432",
      "markText": "贫穷并不仅仅意味着缺钱，它会使人丧失挖掘自身潜力的能力。",
      "totalCount": 10820,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24275985&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=4404&rangeEnd=4432",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932ce071726c119b94961?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=4404&rangeEnd=4432"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24275985_25_8294-8319",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "8294-8319",
      "markText": "他们常常把钱花在昂贵的治疗上，而不是廉价的预防上。",
      "totalCount": 8313,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24275985&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=8294&rangeEnd=8319",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932ce071726c119b94961?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=8294&rangeEnd=8319"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24275985_36_5143-5183",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "5143-5183",
      "markText": "只谈世界上存在什么问题，而不去谈可行的解决方案，这样只能导致社会瘫痪，而非进步。",
      "totalCount": 7824,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24275985&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=5143&rangeEnd=5183",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932ce071726c119b94961?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=5143&rangeEnd=5183"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24275985_21_1151-1214",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "1151-1214",
      "markText": "穷人的出场通常只是作为某种励志剧或悲剧的主人公，或令人钦佩，或惹人怜悯，而不是某种知识的传播者，人们不会向他们咨询想法或计划。",
      "totalCount": 7596,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24275985&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=1151&rangeEnd=1214",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932ce071726c119b94961?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=1151&rangeEnd=1214"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24275985_21_2330-2418",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "2330-2418",
      "markText": "穷人与我们有相同的欲望和弱点，也并不比我们理性多少——正好相反，恰恰因为他们几乎一无所有，我们常常会发现，穷人在做选择时会非常谨慎：为了生存，他们都需要成为精打细算的经济学家。",
      "totalCount": 7392,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24275985&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=2330&rangeEnd=2418",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932ce071726c119b94961?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=2330&rangeEnd=2418"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24275985_24_4726-4779",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "4726-4779",
      "markText": "这再次表明，至少对于这些非常贫穷的城市家庭来说，他们并不是优先选择获取更多的能量，而是获取味道更好的能量。",
      "totalCount": 7350,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24275985&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=4726&rangeEnd=4779",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932ce071726c119b94961?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=4726&rangeEnd=4779"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24275985_24_13946-13992",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "13946-13992",
      "markText": "大量记录显示，发展中国家的穷人会花很多钱来置办婚礼、嫁妆、洗礼等，这很可能是怕丢面子的结果。",
      "totalCount": 7208,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24275985&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=13946&rangeEnd=13992",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932ce071726c119b94961?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=13946&rangeEnd=13992"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24275985_36_1268-1317",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "1268-1317",
      "markText": "这样看来，学生们愿意为了罗西娅而承担一点儿责任，但在面对广泛的全球性问题时，他们就不免有些泄气了。",
      "totalCount": 5904,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24275985&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=1268&rangeEnd=1317",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932ce071726c119b94961?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=1268&rangeEnd=1317"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24275985_25_22050-22089",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "22050-22089",
      "markText": "穷人所陷入的困境与我们其他人的困扰似乎是一样的——缺乏信息、信念不坚定、拖延。",
      "totalCount": 5604,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24275985&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=22050&rangeEnd=22089",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932ce071726c119b94961?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=22050&rangeEnd=22089"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24275985_25_10770-10834",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "10770-10834",
      "markText": "这究竟是怎么回事？为什么穷人有时会拒绝便宜而有效的、能大大改善人们健康的方法，非要花很多钱去买那些毫无帮助的、很可能有害的东西？",
      "totalCount": 5236,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24275985&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=10770&rangeEnd=10834",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932ce071726c119b94961?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=10770&rangeEnd=10834"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24275985_25_7464-7551",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "7464-7551",
      "markText": "低需求量表明，健康问题依旧难以得到根本性的解决：逃出“贫穷陷阱”的“梯子”是存在的，但并非总是放在正确的地方，而且人们似乎不知道怎样踏上“梯子”，或者他们甚至根本不想那样做。",
      "totalCount": 4440,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24275985&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=7464&rangeEnd=7551",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932ce071726c119b94961?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=7464&rangeEnd=7551"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24275985_24_13265-13310",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "13265-13310",
      "markText": "穷人在选择食品时，主要考虑的并不是价格是否便宜，也不是有无营养价值，而是食品的口味怎么样。",
      "totalCount": 4212,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24275985&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=13265&rangeEnd=13310",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932ce071726c119b94961?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=13265&rangeEnd=13310"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24275985_40_14909-14962",
      "chapterUid": 40,
      "range": "14909-14962",
      "markText": "当你想要的一切看上去都很遥远时，你很难感受到动力。将目标设置得更近一些，或许是穷人实现这些目标的有效方式。",
      "totalCount": 3900,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24275985&chapterUid=40&rangeStart=14909&rangeEnd=14962",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932ce071726c119b94961?chapterUid=40&rangeStart=14909&rangeEnd=14962"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24275985_41_845-885",
      "chapterUid": 41,
      "range": "845-885",
      "markText": "这就是真正的企业家精神：如果你所拥有的不多，那么就用你的聪明才智，做到从无到有。",
      "totalCount": 3792,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24275985&chapterUid=41&rangeStart=845&rangeEnd=885",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932ce071726c119b94961?chapterUid=41&rangeStart=845&rangeEnd=885"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24275985_24_15114-15143",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "15114-15143",
      "markText": "总体来说，穷人的首要选择显然是，让自己的生活少一点儿乏味。",
      "totalCount": 3420,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24275985&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=15114&rangeEnd=15143",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932ce071726c119b94961?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=15114&rangeEnd=15143"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24275985_26_24500-24564",
